The '''Senatorial Tombs''' were on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], built as a means of remembering [[Senator/Legends|Senators]] who died while they were in office. The bodies were often interred in [[Carbonite/Legends|carbonite]]. [[Viento]] was one of the Senators buried there.

